WEBVTT

00:04:28.112 --> 00:04:30.710
in shaping features
that we find attractive.

00:04:31.643 --> 00:04:35.500
Estrogen produces features
that signal fertility.

00:04:36.334 --> 00:04:39.284
Men typically find women attractive

00:04:39.308 --> 00:04:43.609
who have elements
of both youth and maturity.

00:04:44.183 --> 00:04:48.156
A face that's too baby-like might
mean that the girl is not yet fertile,

00:04:49.119 --> 00:04:51.092
so men find women attractive

00:04:51.116 --> 00:04:55.352
who have large eyes,
full lips and narrow chins

00:04:55.376 --> 00:04:56.885
as indicators of youth,

00:04:57.700 --> 00:05:01.083
and high cheekbones
as an indicator of maturity.